msgid ""
"All security issues (as well as nomination / removal discussions) become "
"public within approximately fourteen weeks of the fix landing in the LLVM "
"repository. Precautions should be taken to avoid disclosing particularly "
"sensitive data included in the report (e.g. username and password pairs)."
msgstr ""

