#: ../../../Security.rst:186
msgid "What is considered a security issue?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../Security.rst:188
msgid ""
"*FUTURE*: this section will be expanded once the Security Group is formed, "
"and it agrees on an initial security surface area."
